# <p><strong>Description </strong></p>
# <p>This custom transformer cleans all string attributes by performing the followin tasks: </p>
# <ul>
# <li>Remove html directive (ex.: <code>&lt;p&gt;bla bla bla &lt;\p&gt;</code>) so that the string contains only plain text    </li>
# <li>Replace special character (carriage return, line feed, tab) by white spaces</li>
# <li>Replace curly braces {} by parenthesis</li>
# <li>Removing front and trailing white spaces</li>
# <li>Replace multiple white spaces by only one white space</li>
# </ul>
# <p><strong>Input Ports </strong></p>
# <p>INPUT: The input metadata records to clean</p>
# <p><strong>Output Ports </strong></p>
# <p>OUTPUT: The cleaned output metdata records</p>
# <p><strong>Parameters </strong></p>
# <p>None</p>
# TRANSFORMER_END
